# Frontend Rules вЂ” Next.js

## Status

The `frontend/` folder has an **MVP**: home, universities (list + detail with cutoff method filter), majors (paginated), recommend, login/register, profile, chatbot. **Not yet:** admin dashboard, favorites, compare universities. Follow these rules for new pages. Do not use another frontend framework.

## Technology

- Next.js 16 (App Router)
- TypeScript (strict)
- React Server Components by default; mark Client Components with `'use client'`
- Tailwind CSS 4 (via `@import "tailwindcss"` in `globals.css`)
- Environment variables for API base URL (`NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`)

## Environment

```text
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api
```

Never hardcode university/cutoff data in components. All lists and details come from the NestJS API.

